Ken Clark (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ken_Clark_(actor) 0 Kenneth Donovan "Ken" Clark (June 4, 1927 – June 1, 2009) was an American B-movie actor. He appeared in movies in the United States and Europe, including the Secret Agent 077 trilogy. Kenneth_Donovan_"_Ken_"_Clark ( June_4_,_1927 – June_1_,_2009 ) was an_American_B-movie_actor . He appeared in movies in the_United_States and Europe , including the_Secret_Agent_077_trilogy .
